    <physdesc id="aspace_0f1fc61cee6984044105d6d9e9348f70">Correspondence, accession volumes, fund books, and a catalog.</physdesc>
    <abstract id="aspace_ec5f0c51a832442f87e55b502d050214">Records of the Acquisitions Department. include correspondence of Felix Reichmann and Arthur Sweet; miscellaneous correspondence; general correspondence and fund books (1898-1948); accession volumes (1874-1948); Chemistry Library accession books (7 vols., 1927-1962); Latin Seminary accession book, (1892-1914); catalog of the Franz Bopp collection; correspondence with vendors, 1985-1986.</abstract>
